 fullstack capabilities. If you are applying for a specific role, we should focus on the relevant skills and experience.\\n\\nTo proceed, please tell me:\\n\\n1.  Which of these technologies do you have hands-on experience with?\\n2.  Which role are you primarily targeting (Frontend, Backend, or Fullstack)?\\n3.  Do you have a skills section already? If so, please share it.\", \"suggestions\": [\"Show me my current skills section.\", \"Help me create a skills section.\", \"Suggest the best role for me based on my resume.\"], \"detectedIntent\": \"MATCH_JOB\"}','ASSISTANT',5),(23,'GENERAL','aLL of them','2026-03-13 17:48:12.652409',NULL,'USER',5),(24,'GENERAL','Great! Since you have hands-on experience with all the mentioned technologies, we can strategically incorporate them into your resume to showcase your skills effectively. Given the job description\'s focus on early career professionals and the opportunity to be placed in Frontend, Backend, or Fullstack roles, let\'s tailor your resume to highlight your versatility and eagerness to learn.\n\nHere\'s a revised approach:\n\n*   **Skills Section:**\n    *   Create a dedicated \'Technical Skills\' section. List the technologies as follows:\n        *   **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, AngularJS, Vue.js\n        *   **Backend:** Java, Python, Node.js, Express, Spring MVC, Django\n        *   **Databases:** MySQL, PostgreSQL, MongoDB\n        *   **Tools:** Git, Jenkins, Travis\n        *   **Methodologies:** Agile, RESTful API design principles\n*   **Projects/Experience Section:**\n    *   For each project or experience, briefly mention the technologies used and your role (Frontend, Backend, or Fullstack). Quantify your achievements whenever possible (e.g., \'Developed a RESTful API using Spring MVC that reduced latency by 15%\').\n    *   Use action verbs to describe your contributions (e.g., \'Developed\', \'Implemented\', \'Designed\', \'Integrated\').\n*   **Summary/Objective (Optional):**\n    *   C