ventory redistribution engine in Spring Boot that compares live stock levels against zone-specific demand\nthresholds and triggers automated rerouting to high-demand zones, eliminating manual monitoring overhead.\n- Integrated Gemini AI API for predictive demand forecasting across hospital zones; secured multi-admin access using Google\nOAuth 2.0 on a React and Spring Boot full-stack platform.\nTechnical Skills\nLanguages: Java 22, Python, JavaScript (ES6+), TypeScript, SQL, HTML/CSS\nBackend: Spring Boot 3, Spring Security, Spring Data JPA, Spring MVC, Spring AI, LangChain4j, RESTful API Design\nFrontend: React.js, TypeScript\nDatabases: PostgreSQL, MySQL\nDevOps & Cloud: Docker, GitHub Actions, AWS (EC2, S3), Linux, Maven, Postman\nConcepts: Data Structures & Algorithms, OOP, System Design, Microservices, CI/CD, WebSocket/STOMP, Unit Testing (JUnit 5)\nCertifications\n- AWS Academy Cloud Foundations – Amazon Web Services, 2025\n- IBM AI Fundamentals – IBM, 2025\nAchievements & Activities\n- Solved 500+ problems on LeetCode across arrays, trees, graphs, and dynamic programming, consistently optimizing for both time\nand space complexity.\n- Participated in Smart India Hackathon 2024; collaborated in a team of six to design, build, and demo a functional prototype within a\n24-hour deadline.\n','{\"keywordMatch\":{\"score\":\"7/10\",\"explanation\":\"Matched keywords include Java, Spring Boot, React, Docker, and PostgreSQL. Missing keywords depend on the specific job description, but common omissions might include specific cloud certifications beyond the listed AWS Academy, or specific testing frameworks beyond JUnit.\",\"suggestion\":\"Tailor the skills section to match the specific job description, including preferred qualifications and technologies.\"},\"formatting\":{\"score\":\"9/10\",\"explanation\":\"Generally clean formatting with clear section headers and bullet points. Minor improvements could be made to spacing consistency.\",\"suggestion\":\"Ensure consis