 skills. \nAdditional Skills: Casting and controlling, strong knowledge of Microsoft Office and Windows-based applications. \nFields of Interest \n• Electrical power and controlling, Computer, Telecom, Electronics and Networking \nTraining Certifications  \n• OSHA Arabian Safety Training Center \n• Managing Safety Training Ken Institute of Executive learning India \n• Electrical Safety Awareness Mind merge Pvt Ltd  \n• Fire Fighting Mind merge Pvt Ltd \n• Huawei Safety Passport. Huawei eLearning \n• Cyber Security Certificate. Huawei eLearning \n• CCNA (R&S) Training at Corvit system Pvt Ltd Rawalpindi \n• Network security Training at Corvit system Pvt Ltd Rawalpindi \nHobbies & Interests: \nReading, exploring new software’s, Circuit hardware, Netsurfing,  \nPersonal Information: \nPermanent Address:  New Industrial City Riyadh Saudi Arabia                                                                                                         \nNationality:  Pakistani \nReligion:                  Islam \nLanguages:  Urdu, English, Punjabi, Arabic \nFather’s Name:  Muhammad Akram  \nSex:   Male \nMarital Status:  Married \nReferences:  \nAvailable on request. \n \n\n\n--- Additional content recovered from PDF annotations and alternate parser ---\nClass/Course College / Institute Board / University Year\nScore\nB-TECH (hons)\nELECTRICAL\nPreston university\nIslamabad\n3.3 GPA\nB-TECH (Pass)\nPreston university 2014\n3.1 GPA\nDAE/Electrical\nGovt.College of Technology\nAbbottabad\nPeshawar\n2012\n68.76 %\nMetric\n(Science)\nGovt.Centennial Model\nSecondary School\n2009\n62.95 %\nhttp://www.linkedin.com/in/imuhammad-sajid/\nhttps://dn3tzca2xtljm.cloudfront.net/social_icons/16px/linkedin.png','{\"keywordMatch\":{\"score\":\"6/10\",\"explanation\":\"The resume includes keywords like \'Network Maintenance\', \'Troubleshooting\', \'Software Management\', \'AC/DC Power Systems\', and \'Huawei\'. Missing keywords include \'Cloud Computing\', \'Network Security\', \'Automation\', and \'Scripting\'.\",\"suggestion\":\"Incorporate more industry-standard keywords related to cloud, security, and automation to improve relevance.\"},\"formatting\":{\"score\":\"6/10\",\"explanation\":\"The resume has some formatting issues, including dense paragraphs and inconsistent spacing. The resume is also 4 pages long, which is excessive. The format stability is 93%, indicating some potential parsing issues.\",\"suggestion\":\"Use more bullet points, reduce paragraph density, and ensure consistent spacing throughout the resume. Reduce the resume to 1-2 pages.\"},\"sectionCompleteness\":{\"score\":\"8/10\",\"explanation\":\"The resume includes Professional Experience, Academic Records, Technical Skills, Languages, and References. It is missing a Summary section.\",\"suggestion\":\"Add a concise summary or objective at the beginning of the resume to highlight key skills and experience.\"},\"impactScore\":{\"score\":\"6/10\",\"explanation\":\"The resume includes some metrics, such as \'100% completion targets\', \'68.76 %\', and \'62.95 %\'. However, many bullet points lack quantifiable results. For example, \'Performed all types of tickets and shared root causes\' lacks specific impact.\",\"suggestion\":\"Quantify achievements in each role by including specific metrics and outcomes. Use strong action verbs to highlight accomplishments.\"},\"brevity\":{\"score\":\"4/10\",\"explanation\":\"The resume is 4 pages long, which is too long for an experienced candidate. Many bullet points are verbose and could be more concise.\",\"suggestion\":\"Reduce the resume to 1-2 pages by removing redundant information and using concise language. Focus on the most relevant and impactful experiences.\"},\"experienceFit\":{\"score\":\"N/A\",\"explanation\":\"No job description provided for comparison.\",\"suggestion\":\"Advice on how to frame experience to better match the target role level.\"}}','[{\"section\":\"Formatting\",\"priority\":\"high\",\"suggestion\":\"Reduce the r